{"tid":857533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美首次引渡中國間諜 徐彥鈞遭誘捕、起訴","createTime":"2018-10-11T07:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T08:41:05.000Z","uid":105261,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fad0b6db5b70b6c179e0e4b52363b3050648adc7","tid":857533,"uid":105261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1539203698087.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F1539203698087.jpg&h=c236b636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國司法部10日宣布，一名中國情報官員在比利時被捕，9日引渡來美國面臨間諜指控，顯示川普政府打擊中國竊密的努力大幅升級。這名江蘇省國家安全廳的副處長涉竊美國國防部承包商的商業機密，昨天引渡抵美並遭起訴。 <br />\n<br />\n紐約時報報導，中國國安部地區辦公室副主任徐彥鈞 (Yanjun Xu,音譯)遭引渡，是首次中國情報官員被押送至美國面臨起訴。美國官員稱，這名中國官員企圖偷竊奇異航空公司 (GE Aviation)的商業機密，他被誘至比利時以取得奇異航空機密後，在今年4月1日被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/card_img/1050091840396042241/jRLctaK9?format=jpg&amp;name=600x314\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fcard_img%2F1050091840396042241%2FjRLctaK9%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D600x314&h=f66064b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聯邦調查局(FBI)負責反情報的助理局長普利斯塔普 (William Priestap)發表聲明指出，中國情報官員史無前例的引渡，暴露了中國政府直接監控對美國的經濟間諜活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Read-the-criminal-complaint-filed-against-the.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2FRead-the-criminal-complaint-filed-against-the.pdf&d=RVlam78G7dsTti9aOdoEZwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b7cd588d\" target=\"_blank\">http://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Read-the-criminal-complaint-filed-against-the.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n來源:<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/5918983/article-%E7%BE%8E%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E5%BC%95%E6%B8%A1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C-%E5%BE%90%E5%BD%A5%E9%88%9E%E9%81%AD%E8%AA%98%E6%8D%95%E3%80%81%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F5918983%2Farticle-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B8%25A1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25AB%259C-%25E5%25BE%2590%25E5%25BD%25A5%25E9%2588%259E%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AA%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E3%2580%2581%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25B4%2F&d=RVlam78G7dsTti9aOdoEZwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d164a93b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/5918983/article-%E7%BE%8E%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E5%BC%95%E6%B8%A1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C-%E5%BE%90%E5%BD%A5%E9%88%9E%E9%81%AD%E8%AA%98%E6%8D%95%E3%80%81%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4/</a>"},{"pid":"367deabefac0de083e884071cffc7bca11ea714e","tid":857533,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"陸續有嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7728b4b73f8d98bf128e0e5f9adab2c7b525b12","tid":857533,"uid":87723,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:13:59.000Z","msg":"見到XYZ就查一定無死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cbf4f4458a9f74a971350f80d6af4fd4e176672","tid":857533,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:23:29.000Z","msg":"xyz無一個好人"},{"pid":"c82647cba88b6f4d7b2ee15d10ed8acfd4721cd9","tid":857533,"uid":105261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"367deabefac0de083e884071cffc7bca11ea714e","tid":857533,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"陸續有嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:27:06.000Z","msg":"美國中國學生。會唔會好多要 滾出美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81513ceedceb31a65c942a0d7bd84b6c1a1cca50","tid":857533,"uid":3822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:29:3